rivers\n•Contribute to build business/commercial scenario with high level Finance impact including\n•Identify trends and patterns to maximize channels ROI, based on data (e.g. ensure optimize channel mixes)\n•Contribute to Business Development activities where required\n\nWho we’re looking for? Individual Capabilities:\n\n•University Degree in Finance or Data Science or Industry-related Discipline, MBA is a Pro\n•Robust experience of planning and reporting in a complex and international environment (at least 5-7 years)\n•Solid experience in coordinating strategy deployment within an international context (mandatory at least 3 years as BD or management consulting)\n•Business and Industry Savviness\n•Mastering of Financials/ Economics\n•Intellectual Horse Power\n•Effective communication and collaboration skills\n•Strategic planning\n•Cross-functional and critical thinking\n•Analytical Capabilities\n•Initiative & Curiosity\n•Fluency in English and Excellent command in Excel and PowerPoint are mandatory\n\nWhat we offer\n\nOur success depends on the men and women who come to work every single day with a sense of purpose and an appetite for progress. Join PMI and you too can:\n•Seize the freedom to define your future and ours. We’ll empower you to take risks, experiment and explore.\n•Be part of an inclusive and diverse culture, where everyone’s contribution is respected; collaborate with some of the world’s best people and feel like you belong.\n•Pursue your ambitions and develop your skills with a global business – our staggering size and scale provides endless opportunities to progress.\n•Take pride in delivering our promise to society: to improve the lives of a billion smokers.','2020-07-28',29),(55,'Lead Data Scientist','People\'s relationship with food is complicated and we’ve built a platform that simplifies it. Creators of the FoodPrint™, Nutrino uncovers the invisible connections between people and food to empower better nutritional decisions for better health o