arity with modern DS tools and algorithms. You will take part in the design, implementation, and deployment of these algorithms at our huge scale. It\'s most exciting when great models meet huge data, this is what our day to day looks like.\n\nOur tools of trade are (partial list): Spark, Scala, Clojure, Tensorflow, Python, Pandas and friends.\n\nWhat you\'ll do:\nDesign and build data science systems at a very large scale.\nUnderstand the business and product needs and transform them into successful scientific and production ready solutions.\nFitting and taking a leadership position in our growing data science group.\nWhat you have:\nM.Sc/Phd in Computer Science/Physics/Math from a top university. GPA over 85\n5+ years in Data Science/Algorithmic development.\nStrong mathematical/analytical capabilities. Ability to work independently on large projects.\nStrong engineering background. Each member of the group is responsible for both the scientific and the engineering solution.\nAbility to mentor others, work in teams, teach and learn from peers.\nAdvanced proficiency in written and spoken English.\nBonus Points:\nIntroduced by an AppsFlyer team member\nAs a global company operating in 16 countries across 5 continents, we reflect the human mosaic of the diverse and multicultural world in which we live. We ensure equal opportunities for all of our employees and promote the recruitment of diverse talents to our global teams without consideration of race, gender, culture, or sexual orientation. We value and encourage curiosity, diversity, and innovation from all our employees, customers, and partners.\n\n\"As a Customer Obsessed company, we must first be Employee Obsessed. We need to make sure that we provide the team with the tools and resources they need to go All-In.\" Oren Kaniel, CEO','2020-07-07',158),(103,'Data Scientist','מיקום: ת\"א והמרכז\n\nתיאור המשרה:\nלחברה מובילה ומבוססת בתחום ה-Gaming באזור המרכז דרוש/ה Data Scientist.\nהתפקיד כולל מחקר, Design ופיתוח מודלים מורכבים לחיזוי התנהגות. עבודה בחזית הטכנולוגיה, בסביבה צעירה ודינאמית.\n\nדרישות המשרה:\nשנתיים ניסיון בפיתוח אלגוריתמים בתחום ה-Machine Learning / סטטיסטיקה / Data Analysis\nידע חזק ב-Python, R ו-SQL\nיכולת אנליטית מעשית לפתרון בעיות, תרגום דרישות עסקיות לפתרון טכני\nתואר שני במדעי המחשב, הנדסה או סטטיסטיקה\n\nמס\' משרה: 84431','2020-07-11',76),(104,'Data Scientist','Natural Intelligence is a global leader in the online comparison market. Our goal is to simplify decision-making and connect customers with valuable brands.\nOur technology helps millions of consumers around the world make smarter, more confident buying decisions. We do so by creating trusted comparison websites that enable consumers to easily compare products and services online and form high-value relationships with the brands they choose. Our partner brands, some of which are among the most prominent websites worldwide, utilize our platform to maximize their online presence.\nNatural Intelligence is one of the top 50 Google Adwords customers worldwide (#1 in Israel!), with an annual spend of hundreds of millions of dollars.\nWe are looking for a top-notch data scientist to lead the design and implementation of the machine learning models and pipelines in Natural Intelligences experimentation and personalization platforms, using cutting edge technology and tools.\nResponsibilities:\nEnd-to-end ownership, from design to deploy, on models and components of our experimental and personalization systems.\nDevelop algorithm-based systems to support business decisions, taking end-to-end ownership - from design to deploy.\nDevelop models that help us understand and describe our customers e.g. learning how to extract deep interests and tendencies from event streams.\nDevelop production code for both batch and real time models in collaboration with our data and service engineering teams.\nManage an iterative experimentation portfolio, which validates and feeds back into our core customer understandings.\n