ads, supervise the flow of information, and accurately detail all outcomes.\n\nPMF provides the best training in the industry. We offer a range of products to clients, excellent sales support staff, and technology. Our offices which are located in \"Tier 1\" buildings offer a fun and conducive work environment. Not only that, we invest in providing effective leads, and offer daily sales incentives to keep you motivated as you earn.\n\nAs a member of our Sales team, you will represent our firm\'s moral and ethical standards. You will be encouraged to conduct yourself in a professional and courteous manner to clients and co-workers.\n\nWhat you bring\nStrong drive with an ability to learn\nOrganized and detail oriented\nTechnologically savvy; comfortable with Google Sheets, PDF editor, Microsoft Office.\nNatural born leader, competitive mentality.\nFun to be around.\n\nWhat we need:\nA degree in business, finance, economics or really anyone who is a natural born sales person\nAgility, inventiveness, and intellectual curiosity\nA Drive for proactive learning and personal development-you will learn everyday\nAnalytical skills\nUtmost attention to detail\nStrong financial modeling and corporate valuation skills\nValidated good judgement\nYou are able to adhere to strict professional standards in working with clients and colleagues\nWhat you get\nA full-time position Monday through Thursday 4:00 p.m. to 2:00 a.m; the hours are long but the rewards are outstanding, and we promise you\'ll have fun too! (Of course we recognize there\'s life outside the office too so there is flexibility).\nGreat pay structure and earning potential-this is no standard Israeli paycheck.\nFun and energetic atmosphere\n\nWe want you to be yourself. We hire the best, give outstanding training and set you free. If you’re driven to perform, you’ll fit right in. We approach our work daringly, learn quickly, improve constantly, and celebrate our wins at every turn.\n\nPowered by JazzHR\n\nbywmXq0QnL'