ce, color, religion, national origin, sex, sexual orientation, gender identity, veteran status, and disability, or other legally protected status. If you are unable to submit an application because of incompatible assistive technology or a disability, please contact us at talent@ebay.com. We will make every effort to respond to your request for disability assistance as soon as possible.\n\nFor more information see:\n\nEEO is the Law Poster\n\nEEO is the Law Poster Supplement','2020-07-22',184),(2564,'Corporate IT Director','Playtika is looking for Corporate IT Director to join our team!\n\nResponsibilities:\nDevelop and oversee metrics for hardware and software\nEnsuring strategic capacity planning\nManage all or part of the IT department globally, including directly supervising employees, hiring and handling employee concerns and performance\nCommunicate with the technology team and work collaboratively with other departments as required\nDetermine business requirements for IT systems\nImplement technology and security policies in cooperation with the Security team\nDirect and support the implementation of new software and hardware\nIdentify and recommend new technology solutions\n\nדרישות תפקיד\n5+ years of experience in a similar position and at least 3 years in a managerial role in global company\nExperience with SaaS and cloud environment\nExperience with Azure 365 solution\nKnowledge in automation\nManaging a global team of help desk and traditional IT roles in a cloud environment\nEstablished experience in creating work processes and policies in a growing organization\n\nworkהגשת מועמדות','2020-07-24',871),(2565,'Videography Internship','Help spread the Abraham message and convey the wonderful vibe of our hostels, events, and tours! As a videography intern, you’ll be given assignments to record our events, tours, daily hostel life and the hostel surroundings, for marketing purposes. In addition, the job includes all video editing work. We expect our interns t